    CAEN ZLEControlSoftware Rel. 1.0

    Installation and Use Instructions

    -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

    February 2014

    -----------------------------------------------------------------------------


  Content
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  README.txt        :  This file.

  ReleaseNotes.txt  :  Revision History and notes.

   src          :  Source files
   inc          :  Include files

  System Requirements
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  - CAEN Digitizer library
  - Linux OS
  - GNUplot 4.2 (www.gnuplot.org)


  How to get support
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Our Software Support Group is available for questions, support and any other
  software related issue concerning CAEN products; for software support
  visit the page www.caen.it/computing/support.php or send an email to
  support.computing@caen.it


  Syntax
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  ZLEControlSoftware [ConfigFile]
  Default config file is "/etc/ZLEControlSoftware/ZLEControlSoftwareConfig.txt"


  Keyword list and syntax for the configuration file:
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  For configuration file syntax please refer to the ZLEControlSoftware Manual.

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

